metadata.name: Peach Blossoms Study
metadata.description:
This is my very first NFT, minted on my provenance, the pathway launching my roadmap as I burst thru the obstacles and begin this dream.

A panoramic spray of color embellishing the countenance of the coppice, proliferating, accordingly abounding, burgeoning the imagination in such an enchanting season. 

Self curated composite art using my own paintings, drawings, photography, GAN etc. composed in PS often imbued with quantized resonant consciousness frequencies.
